dc_title_s: Topographical map of property for Bergen County Associates, East Rutherford, N.J.
dc_description_s: Topographical map of property for Bergen County Associates, East Rutherford, N.J., including Berry's Creek and Madison Circle Drive.|Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection|Mean High water line as shown on map no 1 of 5, Hackensack River, NJ. Prepared by the Coast and Geodetic Survey for the State of New Jersey to show the mean high water line along the Hackensack River.|Interpolated and compiled from tide controlled photography and supplementd by field surveys by the Coast and Geodetic Survey 1962-1963.|Based on Coast and Geodetic survey Map T 12305 dated 1963.
